<lb ed="L" n="0182b07"/><cb:div type="note"><entry><form>蜻蜓</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL155p0182b0703" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">上倉經切音青下唐丁切音廷蜻蜓蟲名一名蜻蛉</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>磷</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL155p0182b0724" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">良<term rend="no_nor">刅</term>切音吝薄
<lb ed="L" n="0182b08"/>石也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>瞢</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL155p0182b0804" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">謨中切木平聲目不明也</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>黼黻</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL155p0182b0816" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">上匪父切音甫下分物切音弗黼文
<lb ed="L" n="0182b09"/>如斧黻文如兩<anchor xml:id="beg_4d" type="cb-app"/>已<anchor xml:id="end_4d"/>相背</note>。</p></cb:def></entry><entry cb:place="inline"><form>壼</form><cb:def><p xml:id="pL155p0182b0911" rend="margin-left:1em;inline"><note place="inline">苦本切音悃宮中衖謂之壼</note>。</p></cb:def></entry></cb:div></cb:div>
